Katherine Kelly Lang https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Katherine_Kelly_Lang 0 Katherine Kelly Lang (born Katherine Kelly Wegeman; July 25, 1961) is an American actress best known for playing Brooke Logan in the CBS soap opera The Bold and the Beautiful.
